            <head>33. Summary of Conclusions of a <orgName corresp="rec63RdBIrcRXbxHr">Policy Review Committee</orgName> Meeting<note n="1" place="foot" type="source" xml:id="d33fn1">Source: Carter Library, National
                    Security Affairs, Brzezinski Material, Brzezinski Office File, Country Chron
